Title: Welcome stranger!
Descriptions: This one is going to get wet. You've prbably been by the lake a 100 times at this point and never noticed the woman in the water. Let us know if she is still there and we can toss you some coin. -Stinky Pete-
Still working on it? I get it, things are rough outside these walls.

Welcome to Deer Isle, stranger! Surprised and happy you've made it this far. I'm Pete. I'm sort of the middle man here on the island, if you're looking for something or have an item to sell, I'm your man. I broker transactions all over the island, for a small fee. This is my mom's shop, well, used to be a shop. Now she just collects things to help me out and runs the bulletin board for the community. It's where people will post wanted ads if you're looking to make a little money. As you can see, business isn't booming these days. Most people stick to their own out there. Either way, I'm upstairs 24/7 monitoring the air waves and trying to get back online. Stop by some time. Stay safe out there.
